HehascompletedthreeNationalSocialSciencePlanningProjects.Becauseofhisexcellentachievements,hewontheNationalOutstandingTeachingAward&amp;theOutstandingSocialAchievementAwardofZhejiangProvinceformorethantentimes.In2003,HewaslistedamongthefirstnationaluniversityNationalRenownedTeachers.Hepublishedmorethantenbooks,suchasCulturalInterpretationsofContemporaryChineseHistoricalNovels,andover200papersincluding&quot;OntheContradictoryFeaturesof17-yearLiterature&quot;.
